title: KidKraft - Pink Vintage Play Kitchen
description:
Bon Appétit! Our Vintage Kitchen in Pink lets kids pretend they are cooking big feasts for the whole family. With its close attention to detail and interactive features, this adorable kitchen would make a great gift for any of the young chefs in your life.
*Doors open and close
*Oven knobs click and turn
*Cordless phone
*Removable sink for easy cleanup

Dimensions: 33"L x 13.5"W x 35.75"H
Materials: MDF
Country of Origin: China
